    <text id="B0555T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>How forwards a request that two men be arrested and sent to Richmond.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <name type="recipient"><abbr expan="Lieutenatn">Lt.</abbr> D.T. Wells, <abbr
                            expan="Acting Assistant Adjutant General">A.A.A.G.</abbr><lb/><abbr
                            expan="Military District">Milt. Dist.</abbr> Shenandoah<lb/>Winchester,
                            <abbr expan="Virginia">Va</abbr></name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1866-01-29"><abbr expan="January">Jany</abbr> 29 1866</date>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Sir</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I have the honor to submit the enclosed communication of <abbr expan="Colonel"
                        >Col.</abbr> J.W. <unclear>McEnt--</unclear>
                    <abbr expan="Provost">Pro.</abbr> Judge Richmond, <abbr expan="Virginia"
                    >Va.</abbr> as forwarded by <abbr expan="Colonel">Col.</abbr>
                    <abbr expan="Orlando">O.</abbr> Brown, <abbr expan="Assistant Commissioner"
                        >Asst. Commr.</abbr> Bureau of Refugees, Freedmen &amp; Abandoned Lands,
                    at Richmond, <abbr expan="Virginia">Va</abbr> with the request that the freedmen
                    George Whit &amp; John Whit may be arrested and sent to <abbr
                        expan="Colonel">Col.</abbr> O. Brown <abbr expan="Assistant Commissioner"
                        >Asst. Commr.</abbr> at Richmond, <abbr expan="Virginia">Va</abbr>.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>I am, Sir &amp;c</salute>
                    <signed>W. Storer How<lb/><abbr expan="Captain">Capt</abbr> &amp;c</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
